abstract: Europa League round of 32 qualifying teams now include Liverpool, Tottenham and Schalke; other qualifying news noted.
lead_paragraph: Liverpool, Tottenham and Schalke, all former winners of the UEFA Cup, advanced to the Europa League round of 32.

headline.main: Eleven Teams Advance to Europa League Round of 32
